      "step_index": 4,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "- **Amide / hydrazide motif:**  \n  - `C(=O)NN(...)` = **acyl hydrazide** (amide carbonyl + adjacent nitrogens).  \n  - One **N\u2013H** present (H-bond donor).  \n  - One **N-methyl** on the terminal hydrazide N (`NN(C)...`) = \u201ctertiary\u201d at that N but **still part of an amide-like system**.",
