    {
      "step_id": "a877b546",
      "step_index": 5,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "- **Strong EWG / lipophilicity booster:**  \n  - **Trifluoromethyl** group (`C(F)(F)F`) increases lipophilicity and often increases CYP binding affinity.",
